you've seen them on the wall in your
office building or something like that.

45
00:02:07.830 --> 00:02:09.240
This is a router.

46
00:02:09.240 --> 00:02:12.160
On the back, it's got an antennae,
since it's a wireless router.

47
00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:13.960
On the back, again,
it's got ethernet ports.

48
